 Davido and DMW Female Artist Liya The artist under the record label of Davido Music Worldwide (DMW) Liya has been reportedly arrested by the Nigerian police after being raided alongside over 100 people for flout lockdown rules. According to reports, Liya and other 237 club-goers flaunted the COVID-19 protocols in Lagos where the government has set aside some protocols to prevent the spread of the virus. 